These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different games are played: bridge, go, poker, billiard
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, family, superhero, western
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, rabbit, rat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, parkour, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, skateboard, snowmobile, train
 1. the person playing bridge is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 3. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 4. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the person watching western movies is the person watching western movies##1
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
 8. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 9. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
11. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
12. the owner of the rabbit is between the person watching superhero movies and the owner of the dog##2
13. the person playing poker is the person driving the train##1
14. the person driving the snowmobile is the person playing go##1
15. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the person playing go##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |     4      |
| Game           | bridge | poker | billiard  | go    |
| Movie-Genre   | family     | western   | superhero  | adventure  |
| Pet           | dog        | rabbit    | rat        | chinchilla |
| Sport         | sailing    | golf      | biathlon   | parkour    |
| Transport     | quad-bike  | train     | skateboard | snowmobile |

